License: MIT

===================
mcspy
===================

A Python Library for Mobile Crowdsensing Problems,
with random, Epsilon-Greedy and New_MAB methods to build a MCS system and its group.

----------------
Installation
----------------

::

    pip install mcspy

----------------
Author contact
----------------

Han Yaohui

1407210129@csu.edu.cn

